Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.81,0:00:21.90,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Kono basho de deau subete mo
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.65,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Tatoe chigau sekai demo
Dialogue: 3,0:00:25.29,0:00:32.80,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Doko ni itemo kono omoi wa yuruganai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:41.74,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Mune wo chikuri to sasu itami
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.34,0:00:48.06,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore mo warau shiawase na mono tachi e
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.64,0:00:50.17,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Se wo mukeyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:58.68,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Touzen no kurushimi wo unmei ga sasou
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.51,0:01:03.97,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Furuedasu ashi ga oboeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.83,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Kakushin ni
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.58,0:01:10.53,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Yume dake ja mamorenai
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.27,0:01:13.44,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Toyoranai chikara
Dialogue: 3,0:01:13.07,0:01:19.58,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Ima kono te de shirukara
Dialogue: 4,0:01:19.52,0:01:23.33,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Mayowanai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:18.26,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Be it the reason I live here.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.81,0:00:21.90,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}or be it everything I encountered here.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.65,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if it were a different world,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:25.29,0:00:32.80,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}no matter where I am, \Nthis feeling won't be swayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:41.74,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The pain from the heart getting pierced,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.34,0:00:48.06,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}that should be directed at \Nthose fortunate people with a smiling face.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.64,0:00:50.17,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Turn your back on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:58.68,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Fate beckons the obvious suffering,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.51,0:01:03.97,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}the trembling feet remember
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.83,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}a certainty now.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.58,0:01:10.53,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Dreams alone are not enough to protect
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.27,0:01:13.44,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}such an unreliable power.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:13.07,0:01:19.58,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I will now see for myself with these hands.
Dialogue: 4,0:01:19.52,0:01:23.33,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}No more hesitation.
